title: Want to join a club?
body: Hey this club is for gold-plat players that rank frequently and able to see who is online and able to make a premade team for dynamic queue. Silver players can join depending if they are low/high silver. The club name is Acceleratex and tag is XLR8x. Add Deadshotx if you want to join!!
